#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Manage your agreements 📝</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Gérez vos accords 📝</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Managing Commissions  👩‍🎨</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Gérer les commissions 👩‍🎨</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Marketing Automation</strong>: Engage potential buyers with "
"personalized campaigns and newsletters."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Marketing Automation</strong> : engagez des acheteurs potentiels "
"avec des campagnes personnalisées et des newsletters."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Memberships &amp; Subscriptions</strong>: Offer exclusive content, "
"VIP access, and limited-event participation."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Abonnements et adhésions</strong> : offrez du contenu exclusif, un "
"accès VIP et un accès à des événements en nombre limité."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.ir_ui_view_3577
msgid ""
"<strong>My Gallery</strong>\n"
"                      <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ma galerie</strong>\n"
"                      <br/>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>POS</strong>: Enables fast, in-store transactions for walk-in "
"customers."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Point de Vente</strong> : permet des transactions rapides en magasin "
"pour les clients de passage."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Projects</strong>: Manage large-scale exhibitions or arts festivals, "
"integrating planning, tasks, and team collaboration."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Projets</strong> : gérez des expositions à grande échelle ou des "
"festivals artistiques en intégrant la planification, les tâches et la "
"collaboration d’équipe."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Publish the Artwork</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Publier l’œuvre d’art</strong> :"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Purchase</strong>: Helps manage vendor relationships and streamline "
"procurement processes."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Achats</strong> : aide à gérer les relations fournisseurs et à "
"rationaliser les processus d’approvisionnement."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Receive the Artwork</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Recevoir l’œuvre d’art</strong> :"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Sales</strong>: Validates orders, creates custom quotations, and "
"streamlines the sales process."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Ventes</strong> : valide les commandes, crée des devis personnalisés "
"et rationalise le processus de vente."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Track New Artwork Opportunities</strong>:"
msgstr "<strong>Suivre de nouvelles opportunités d’œuvres d’art</strong> :"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.ir_ui_view_1680
msgid "<strong>We are MyGallery.</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>Nous sommes MyGallery.</strong>"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Website &amp; eCommerce</strong>: Your gallery’s online storefront, "
"where customers can browse and purchase artworks anytime, anywhere."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Site Web et eCommerce</strong> : la boutique en ligne de votre "
"galerie, où les clients peuvent consulter et acheter des œuvres d’art à tout "
"moment et partout."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A potential buyer has inquired about an artwork—how exciting! Let’s go "
"through the steps to turn this inquiry into a sale."
msgstr ""
"Un acheteur potentiel a fait une demande concernant une œuvre d’art - quelle "
"bonne nouvelle ! Parcourons les étapes pour transformer cette demande en "
"vente."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Accept various payment methods, including cash, credit cards, and mobile "
"payments."
msgstr ""
"Acceptez différents modes de paiement, notamment les espèces, les cartes de "
"crédit et les paiements mobiles."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Acquiring new pieces for your gallery is seamless with <strong>CRM</strong> "
"and the <strong>Purchase App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"L’acquisition de nouvelles œuvres pour votre galerie est simplifiée avec "
"<strong>CRM</strong> et l’app <strong>Achats</strong>."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add detailed product pages with high-resolution images, descriptions, and "
"pricing."
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez des pages produits détaillées avec des images haute résolution, des "
"descriptions et des prix."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add tags to your contacts to make it easy to sort between Artists and "
"Customers"
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez des étiquettes à vos contacts afin de faciliter la distinction entre "
"artistes et clients"

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add the artwork as a product, specifying quantity, price, and expected "
"delivery date."
msgstr ""
"Ajoutez l’œuvre d’art comme produit, en indiquant la quantité, le prix et la "
"date de livraison prévue."

#. module: gallery
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:gallery.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adding Artwork to Your Collection 🎨"
msgstr "Ajouter des œuvres d’art à votre collection 🎨"

